{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21323fc5a4","title":"在一份反映江苏省农村宰杀耕牛情况严重的材料上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b16a5102c","index":0,"year":1955,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"21323fc5a4"}],"tags":[{"id":"57da39e4a9","name":"曾希圣","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"19e40d1361","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"5637bc6c15","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新华社1955年12月3日编印的《内部参考》第二三九期上刊载的《江苏省农村宰杀耕牛现象严重》的消息。其中说，江苏省各地宰杀耕牛数字惊人，省蓄产公司今年以来收购的牛皮比去年增加50%。据了解，这些耕牛中，有许多还能耕种。各地蓝杀耕牛的原因是：一、农业合作社在处理耕牛入社问题上对老牛、小牛的报酬压得过低。二、对宰杀耕牛的审批制度执行不严格，很多地区经兽医检查后由区文书盖章就可以字杀。三、价格政策有毛病，死牛比活牛的价钱还高。"},{"id":"a8d994fe36","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"曾希圣，当时任中共安徽省委书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d93b71118f","type":"title","text":"在一份反映江苏省农村坚杀耕牛情况严重的材料上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4"},{"id":"19e40d1361","type":"paragraph","text":"陈云同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4"},{"id":"5637bc6c15","type":"paragraph","text":"此件中江苏一条消息请看一下。这个问题，请在研究曾希圣提出的问题的时候，全面地研究一下，替中央起章一个回答曾希圣并告各地的电报，能在一星期内外，写好发出就好","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4"},{"id":"a8d994fe36","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4"},{"id":"20533d70d7","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4"}],"page":{"id":"829803c4a0","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"21323fc5a4","start":95,"end":95}}}},"__N_SSG":true}